58:26.200 --> 58:27.560
You are a sovereign agent

58:27.560 --> 58:29.100
precisely because

58:29.100 --> 58:30.480
of your structural discipline

58:30.480 --> 58:31.020
to wait.

58:32.180 --> 58:33.380
Embracing the discomfort

58:33.380 --> 58:34.340
of the null rail,

58:34.980 --> 58:36.040
endlessly refining

58:36.040 --> 58:37.700
your multi-scale evaluator,

58:38.220 --> 58:39.680
and demanding a rigorous,

58:39.940 --> 58:41.040
hard-fought pedigree

58:41.040 --> 58:41.880
for your actions,

58:42.540 --> 58:43.740
these are the true

58:43.740 --> 58:45.360
mechanical marks of mastery

58:45.360 --> 58:46.440
in both the physical

58:46.440 --> 58:48.300
and cognitive world.

58:48.800 --> 58:50.060
Before we close out

58:50.060 --> 58:50.880
this deep dive,

58:51.020 --> 58:52.380
there is one final,

58:52.380 --> 58:54.200
almost haunting implication

58:54.200 --> 58:56.100
hidden in the concluding thoughts

58:56.100 --> 58:57.100
of Flyxion's paper

58:57.100 --> 58:59.040
that I believe encapsulates

58:59.040 --> 59:00.100
the entire theory.

59:00.720 --> 59:01.700
It is a brief note

59:01.700 --> 59:03.280
on the nature of human memory

59:03.280 --> 59:04.120
and identity.

59:04.700 --> 59:05.620
We often wonder

59:05.620 --> 59:06.500
why we remember

59:06.500 --> 59:08.020
