59:14.260 --> 59:15.220
Flyxion proposes

59:15.220 --> 59:16.780
a mechanical reason for this.

59:17.240 --> 59:18.500
Only events that possess

59:18.500 --> 59:19.180
a rich,

59:19.420 --> 59:20.280
highly dimensional

59:20.280 --> 59:21.600
admissibility token

59:21.600 --> 59:22.760
are written permanently

59:22.760 --> 59:23.940
into the core structures

59:23.940 --> 59:24.500
of memory.

59:24.940 --> 59:25.300
Meaning,

59:25.780 --> 59:27.180
the events with the longest

59:27.180 --> 59:28.100
null durations.

59:28.560 --> 59:28.960
Yes.

59:29.600 --> 59:31.140
The moments in your life

59:31.140 --> 59:32.220
where you were forced

59:32.220 --> 59:33.020
to wait the longest,

59:33.380 --> 59:34.840
the moments where the environment

59:34.840 --> 59:35.600
