59:35.740 --> 59:36.560
where you struggled,

59:36.940 --> 59:38.180
where you had to desperately

59:38.180 --> 59:39.680
escalate your resolution,

59:40.140 --> 59:41.080
zooming in and out,

59:41.480 --> 59:42.640
feeling the microtensions

59:42.640 --> 59:43.820
of a complex problem

59:43.820 --> 59:45.300
before you finally achieved

59:45.300 --> 59:46.260
the structural click.

59:46.880 --> 59:47.960
Those are the events

59:47.960 --> 59:49.360
that leave the deepest,

59:49.640 --> 59:50.860
most permanent traces

59:50.860 --> 59:51.440
in your mind

59:51.440 --> 59:52.220
because they required

59:52.220 --> 59:53.120
the highest degree

59:53.120 --> 59:54.180
of structural discipline

59:54.180 --> 59:55.280
to resolve.

59:55.420 --> 59:56.200
And conversely,

59:56.720 --> 59:58.000
the moments of immediate,

59:58.440 --> 01:00:00.380
easy, automatic action,

01:00:01.120 --> 01:00:02.860
the frictionless commutes,

01:00:03.340 --> 01:00:05.080
